channel.title: The Dengineers
channel.desc: Nine-year-old Rufus loves climbing and playing, but he isn't always able to join his friends when they are out having fun. Rufus has leukaemia and regularly has to go to hospital for treatment and check-ups, meaning he often misses out on the adventures he loves. The experts bring the adventure to him by giving him his very own adventure den.
